casebody.data:
Springer, Respondent, v. Bien et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 10, 1890.)

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

F. Bien, for appellants. J. E. Burke, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion to withdraw appeal granted, with $10 costs. Motion for a new trial denied, with costs. See 10 N. Y. Supp. 530.
